  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Patient Experience Questionnaire - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_patient_experience_questionnaire">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Patient Experience Questionnaire</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_patient_experience_questionnaire">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Patient Experience Questionnaire</xref>
 is a self-completed questionnaire relating to a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
's experience of an 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_service">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Service</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_patient_experience_questionnaire">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Patient Experience Questionnaire</xref>
 is made up of two parts:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <p>Assessment with separate questions for:</p>
         <ul>
            <li>
               <p>Choice</p>
            </li>
            <li>
               <p>Satisfaction</p>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Treatment.</p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
For further information on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_patient_experience_questionnaire">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Patient Experience Questionnaires</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/mental-health/adults/iapt/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Adult Improving Access to Psychological Therapies programme</xref>
.  </p>
  <p> </p>

